Description:
Room to Move
This is a lovely home well worth an inspection.
-3 bedroom
-37 squares under roof, 23 squares liveable
-Decking all around the house
-Enclosed BBQ area
- Fully renovated kitchen with new appliances, dishwasher, black wood cupboards
-Ducted evap. cooling and 2 x Inverter systems plus ceiling fans and a big wood heater.
-11 foot ceiling with decorative cornices.
-Formal lounge and separate dining and family room
-3 bedrooms all carpeted with built in robes & ceiling fans. All quality drapes & fittings.
-Bathroom renovated with shower recess, bath, tiled floors and walls
-2 Megs stock & domestic from channel. Channel water services all the 2.2 acres
with plenty of sprinkler points & garden taps. 3 x 23,000 litre rain water tanks service only the house through a pressure pump with plenty of catchment area to keep tanks full.
- Solar power 3kw solar set up Zero power bill on a six year locked in 66c rebate.
- Septic tank new environmental system
- Rural fencing all around.
- Shed 33m x 8m, concrete floor, look up shed has 3 phase power and work shop.
Great home that the owner has put a lot of time and effort in.
A Great Family Home!!

Description:
"Waringa" Koonoomoo
32.42 Ha (80 Acres) of a most picturesque rural property close to the Murray River & bushlands. The property is well treed, fully lasergraded & sown to pasture, 2 acres of grapes (different varieties) & 240 Ml licence from irrigation bore (connected to 7KW solar power system) Spacious 3 BR BV residence, 2 living areas, air conditioning & S/C heating. Double lockup garage plus double carport, as new secure workshop with concrete floor & 3 phase power & 2 x mach sheds.
"Waringa" has a "great feel" about it & is worthy of your inspection & consideration.

Description:
Appealing Lifestyle Property
Beautifully presented four bedroom family home with room to move. Set on a 5059 square metre block with established lawns and gardens, this property has plenty of appeal. Neat kitchen featuring a gas cooktop, electric oven and a massive walk in pantry/preparation room. Adjoining meals area with access to rear verandah. Large lounge with lovely timber floors and reverse cycle split system air conditioner. Feature solid fuel heater in addition to under-floor, ducted, natural gas heating and gas infinite hot water service. Separate large, family/rumpus room. Four generous bedrooms, all with built in robes, and main bedroom with walk in robe and ensuite. Fully insulated in ceiling and both internal and external walls. Verandah all around, with ramp access at rear and a handy screened area for insect free enjoyment. 2 kw solar electricity system. Filtered tank water is supplied to the house and a communal bore waters the gardens. 9 metre by 20 metre colorbond shed with three roller doors, concrete floor, power, water, shower and toilet. Caravan port, wood shed and garden shed. Very neat and established gardens and lawns and impressive vegetable garden. Great location, only 10kms from Cobram!
Appealing on many levels - Well worth an inspection!

Description:
Rare Property with Sheep Wash Creek lease.
The perfect place to escape from it all! Superb 1.7 hectare block offering peace and privacy plus superb bushland and creek outlook. An additional 1.9 hectares of grazing land is included on a new five year lease. Renovated, spacious four bedroom and ensuite brick veneer home, freshly painted and including a new kitchen. Cosy, solid fuel heater plus reverse cycle split system air conditioning. Entertaining patio. Domestic bore to house and watering system. 18 solar electricity panels ( 3 kilowatt) with a 5 kilowatt inverter system, contracted for another ten years at 70 cents rebate. Machinery shed. Good fencing around house. Plenty of native trees.
A very unique and secluded property!

Description:
PERFECT STARTER DAIRY FARM
This exceptional 116 acre dairy farm is located on some of the best soil types in the Goulburn Valley (Yarroweyah area). The farm is approx. 80% lasered with large bay outlets with a conservative 1.7 D/S complimented by a 125 meg spear point bore, central gravel laneways, stock troughs and exceptional shedding. Dairy consists of a 12 S/O dairy, feed system, 3rd line wash, plate cooler, Bonlac feed system with roller and dispenser. This tastefully renovated period style homestead has 3 bedrooms, brand new kitchen & bathroom, quality floor coverings, wood fire and ducted cooling. You won't find better. Also 170 megs HR & 85 megs LR water available at C.M.V.

Description:
Cute Country Cottage on 5 Acres
Appealing, renovated two bedroom cottage on approximately five acres. Features high ceilings, a wide verandah and a cosy open plan kitchen/meals/lounge with electric cooking, plenty of cupboards and a reverse cycle air condtioner. Rainwater tanks supply the house and channel water is also available if required. Outside there is a 10m x 6m shed with concrete floor and power, a 3m x 3m garden shed, loading race and yards, horse wash bay and two dog kennels and runs. Good fencing, plenty of space for parking and a great paddock set-up for a few cows or horses. Stock and domestic water allowance included. Handy to both Cobram and Katamatite.
A well-presented property at a great price! Inspect now!

Description:
Outstanding Hobby or Lifestyle Block ~ 31 Acres
Hobby farm with income and only 12 kilometres from Cobram. 2 x approximate 15 acre blocks totalling approx 31 acres with features including new front boundary fence, 2 new entrances and gates, improvements, s & d bore with electric pump and new 7.5 KVA generator, 10m x 10m shed with cement floor and solar power. Perfect set up for weekender with combustion stove, sink, some cupboards , work bench and rota loo. Lots of established native trees planted around the shed and providing a lovely, private setting. Dams for water storage. Contractor cutting hay for the last 2 years has produced 160 large bales, selling at approximately $50 each - they pick up- no work for you. There is at least a 5 acre area above the flood overlay, suitable as your new home site (STCA) and power is only 200 metres away.
This is a very quiet and peaceful block - a great place to unwind! Very realistic vendor, with price to sell quickly!
Also included ride on lawnmower, generator and sundries.
